Added ability to delete content from memory. Important!: The object should not be accessed as this method badly corrupts the memory!

ONLY USE ANTIEXPLOIT.OVERWRITEMEMORY WITH OBJECTS THAT CAN BE LEN(). Else it may cause python.exe to crash. If needed first del the object in question run python garbage collecter and then use the previously saved atributes to remove from the memory.
Solve issues - made memory clearing safer!
Solved some extra complications at low level memory mode. Figured out how to use WSL to use this app on linux.
